hotel on the corner.

20
00:03:08,762 --> 00:03:10,930
Look at that
photo on the left...

21
00:03:11,014 --> 00:03:12,974
That there's the bounty we want.

22
00:03:13,058 --> 00:03:14,934
And the girl on the right
is the bounty hunter

23
