46
00:04:24,629 --> 00:04:26,715
Do you... hate men?

47
00:04:26,798 --> 00:04:28,842
No, I don't.

48
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,846
I swear, I don't.

49
00:04:34,055 --> 00:04:37,017
[NADIE] I'll admit, I was the
one who suggested you buy a book

50
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:40,270
to give you something to
do on the long bus ride...

51
00:04:40,353 --> 00:04:43,023
But why'd you pick one
that was so trashy?

52
00:04:43,106 --> 00:04:44,816
Because the name
was like yours.

53
00:04:44,899 --> 00:04:47,610
Funny 'cause that's the part
that pissed me off most...

54
00:04:47,694 --> 00:04:49,654
Even more so with
the guy's name.

55
00:04:49,738 --> 00:04:50,405
Miguel?

56
00:04:50,488 --> 00:04:52,782
[NADIE grunts]

57
00:04:52,866 --> 00:04:54,034
[MIGUEL]
'Ey Nadie!

58
00:04:54,117 --> 00:04:55,994
Nadie, is that you?!

59
00:04:56,077 --> 00:04:58,788
[NADIE] No... can't be.

60
